API Endpoints
Method	Path	Auth	Description
GET	/flights/health	Public	Health check
GET	/flights/search?departureCity=&destinationCity=&travelDate=&passengers=	Guest OK	Search available flights
GET	/flights/{id}	Public	Get flight details
GET	/flights	ADMIN	List all flights
POST	/flights	ADMIN	Create flight
PATCH	/flights/{id}/status?status=DELAYED	ADMIN	Update flight status
DELETE	/flights/{id}	ADMIN	Delete flight
Sample Search (guest — no JWT needed)
GET http://localhost:8083/flights/search?departureCity=Delhi&destinationCity=Mumbai&travelDate=2026-03-10&passengers=1

Startup Order
Eureka (8761) → auth-service (8081) → user-service (8082) → flight-service (8083) → api-gateway (8080)

Swagger UI
http://localhost:8083/swagger-ui.html

# Search 5 flights (Delhi → Mumbai, 2026-03-10)
GET http://localhost:8083/flights/search?departureCity=Delhi&destinationCity=Mumbai&travelDate=2026-03-10&passengers=1

# Search Mumbai → Delhi
GET http://localhost:8083/flights/search?departureCity=Mumbai&destinationCity=Delhi&travelDate=2026-03-10&passengers=2

# Next day flights
GET http://localhost:8083/flights/search?departureCity=Delhi&destinationCity=Mumbai&travelDate=2026-03-11&passengers=1

# DELAYED flight NOT in search results (status filter)
GET http://localhost:8083/flights/search?departureCity=Delhi&destinationCity=Chennai&travelDate=2026-03-10&passengers=1
# → returns 2 SCHEDULED flights (AI-902, 6E-902); AI-901 (DELAYED) excluded ✓

# Admin: view ALL flights including DELAYED/CANCELLED
GET http://localhost:8083/flights  (requires ADMIN JWT)
